OL,3,CMan 'angry' after mother on trolley
OL,4,Cfor 48 hours at Sussex hospital
OL,6,FA man from Eastbourne says he's angry
OL,7,Fhis elderly mother had to wait two
OL,8,Fdays on a trolley in A&E, before being
OL,9,Fadmitted to a ward.
OL,11,FMark Wilson's mother was left on
OL,12,Ftrolley in a corridor at the Royal
OL,13,FSussex County Hospital for nearly 48
OL,14,Fhours when she'd suffered a mini-
OL,15,Fstroke.
