OL,3,CMan 'angry' after mother on trolley
OL,4,Cfor 48 hours at Sussex hospital
OL,6,FMark said he doesn't blame staff at
OL,7,Fthe Royal Sussex County Hospital in
OL,8,FBrighton and can't fault any doctors
OL,9,Ffor his mother's treatment. But, he
OL,10,Fthinks they are overburdened with
OL,11,Fpatients, adding that the hospital
OL,12,Fneeds more resources.
OL,14,FMark Wilson said: "I actually felt
OL,15,Fquite angry really that she's gone
OL,16,Fthrough that. It's a 71-year-old woman
OL,17,Fon a trolley in A&E, no dignity,
OL,18,Fnothing there.
