OL,3,CMan 'angry' after mother on trolley
OL,4,Cfor 48 hours at Sussex hospital
OL,6,F"She just had a stroke and people that
OL,7,Fhave strokes are meant to be kept
OL,8,Fcalm. She wasn't being kept calm in my
OL,9,Fview, more stress added to her that
OL,10,Fshe didn't need."
OL,12,FIt comes as junior doctors started a 5-
OL,13,Fday strike, in a long running pay
OL,14,Fdispute with the Government. It's the
OL,15,F11th walkout since industrial action
OL,16,Fbegan.
