OL,3,CMan 'angry' after mother on trolley
OL,4,Cfor 48 hours at Sussex hospital
OL,6,FDr Andy Heeps, Chief Operating Officer
OL,7,Fat UH Sussex said: "When our hospitals
OL,8,Fare so busy, staff can struggle to
OL,9,Fmove patients into the right ward
OL,10,Fspace because beds are not available -
OL,11,Fthat is a poor experience for
OL,12,Fpatients, and we would apologise to
OL,13,Fanyone who is affected in this way.
OL,15,F"Our teams do brilliant work to ensure
OL,16,Fthat patients still receive the care
OL,17,Fthey need, from the right specialists,
OL,18,Feven in A&E but we know this is not
OL,19,Fwhat people should expect.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
