OL,3,CMan 'angry' after mother on trolley
OL,4,Cfor 48 hours at Sussex hospital
OL,6,F"The situation in our hospitals
OL,7,Freflects pressures across the whole
OL,8,Fhealth and care system, and we are
OL,9,Factively working with our partners to
OL,10,Fbetter manage how people can get the
OL,11,Fcare they need, in the right place, as
OL,12,Fquickly as possible."
